{"tid":1908524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：口頭訓斥是最輕微處分 不會入簿 無礙仕途","createTime":"2020-03-03T10:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T11:01:56.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a3adbe4211d3c30b7f938d9625f6804e3c911a3a","tid":1908524,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:42:46.000Z","msg":"警務處處長鄧炳強今日表示，就近月的抗爭活動中，警隊督導人員曾「訓斥」21名警員，包括涉嫌在11月駕駛警方電單車衝入人群示威者的交通警，以及兩名曾在執法時不適當展示他人記者身份證（致洩露記者私隱）的警員。但有資深警官指出，口頭訓斥是違規警員的處分之中最輕微的，甚至有機會不用寫進俗稱「行為簿」的警員服務紀錄，即是不用作書面紀錄。故警員若違規後僅被上司「訓斥」，很多時都無礙仕途，有可能照樣升職。從另一角度看，「訓斥」是最容易放生違規警員的處分。<br />\n<br />\n根據《警察（紀律）條例》，警方的紀律處分，由輕微至嚴重懲處依次為警誡、譴責、嚴厲譴責、沒收不多於1個月的薪金、降級、立即辭職、迫令退休及革職，條例之中，沒有鄧炳強所謂「訓斥」一項。<br />\n有警官解釋，俗稱口頭警告的「訓斥」其實是最輕微的處分，訓斥也分兩種，第一種較輕微，是由警員直屬上司作出的口頭警告，毋須寫進「行為簿」；第二種「訓斥」則較嚴重，須寫進「行為簿」，即成為一個書面紀錄，但若上司打算把訓斥一事寫進警員行為簿，須通知有關警區的指揮官。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士補充，若警員違規行為比以上更嚴重，但尚未到達可作刑事檢控的地步，例如<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警員與黑幫懷疑過往甚密</span></span></strong>、<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或未經上司許可擅自借高利貸，警方便有權對有關警員作出紀律聆訊。聆訊的結果除可帶來降職、革職等嚴重處分外，更可能影響到違規警員離開警隊後，不能獲得原有的福利如長俸等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200302/OVA4ZTCBSOFIPI4EBW5XWYGWUQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200302%2FOVA4ZTCBSOFIPI4EBW5XWYGWUQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=2a195b26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200302%2FOVA4ZTCBSOFIPI4EBW5XWYGWUQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=362c2b8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200302/OVA4ZTCBSOFIPI4EBW5XWYGWUQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"30fc3ab8160af40d108c1079aebbe4157019f304","tid":1908524,"uid":19055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"冇後果點解唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e52122225f2f10644eb8147161323e31695374","tid":1908524,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"我地已經口頭訓斥過所有被捕手足 (斥責佢地太唔小心比狗咬)<br />\n要求警謊立即釋放所有被捕人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf302fd45a82b36241cc6feac834c29dbbd58387","tid":1908524,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4892569f0ead626a16114a74c9e1e040e2f4df","tid":1908524,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:01:56.000Z","msg":"你地冇做錯<br />\n最錯俾人影到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}